instagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=JCdyIS5F1tb7mkHJkFZiUw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwrpS_OM8J_nJcAsaJtjOEwU7n6O4DM0Wz7LGJIiEpt1A&amp;oe=69CA01EE" alt="Slide 3 fra @damienhirst" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656001473_18442129384112163_5299772101862074650_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1OTMxNjE4NDczNTAyNzk2NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=n7XKx_4qqQQQ7kNvwE5iq9N&amp;_nc_oc=AdocwkktFvkoqoJGaz4SyU8ibhhqqRCs2m9KfDxm-ClvJvtOjj-mBAUHMU7xExkqVsA&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=JCdyIS5F1tb7mkHJkFZiUw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzGPixM3RUC2GzfL3gaNtoouh3Db5yXg1P5qd9PAKCfZQ&amp;oe=69CA131A" alt="Slide 4 fra @damienhirst" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (8 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@damienhirst</strong></p><p>Introducing: The ‘Triple Trouble’ catalogue 📚<br/>
<br/>
Published to accompany the exhibition of the same name, this catalogue documents individual and collaborative works by @obeygiant, @damienhirst, and @invaderwashere.<br/>
<br/>
Presenting all works from the show in full-colour reproduction, it showcases familiar motifs, such as Fairey’s Obey iconography, Hirst’s spots and cabinets and Invader’s Space Invader mosaics, reconfigured in provocative and playful ways.<br/>
<br/>
 📍Explore the book via our link in bio.<br/>
<br/>
🖼️ Don’t miss your chance to see the artworks in person, at the ‘Triple Trouble’ exhibition at Newport Street Gallery. The show is running until 29 March.<br/>
<br/>
🎨 Original artworks from the exhibition are available by application on HENI Primary via our link in bio until 29 March.<br/>
<br/>
#HENI #Art #ArtBook #TripleTrouble #Exhibition</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWPDB85DEmA/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
