ninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=JCdyIS5F1tb7mkHJkFZiUw&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfwAO0OL97av7xd_jLnmQzyHl06ksXrR9QDzaIEP0Dqu0Q&amp;oe=69CA0949" alt="Slide 3 fra @damienhirst" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/650250193_18566606905061635_7340805818950431463_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1MjY1MDcwMDkxMjQ3NjcxNg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=pKLaEqNvSKcQ7kNvwFGX-1j&amp;_nc_oc=Adpi4OGhUOliqQCs0QH7sjzD1Y66gk_h-Way8VQKZNpoknh7Zo4IHTLJVnCQcCs5IQg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=JCdyIS5F1tb7mkHJkFZiUw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afx3-cPaxJgvfWEgsCRlRE6idb-5ocatSHdI6vI1Zk0YXA&amp;oe=69CA2F2A" alt="Slide 4 fra @damienhirst" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (8 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@damienhirst</strong></p><p>My and @obeygiant’s new print release is available on @HENI Editions until 16 March at 17:00 GMT via the link in bio.<br/>
<br/>
I love working with Shepard, he’s a great artist and a great human being and there aren’t many people around who have both those qualities never mind artists and he gives a shit more than most in a world where hope is in short supply, oh and he’s a punk!<br/>
<br/>
Together we have created magical paintings that are filled with the joy of life and the power of good in the constant battle between good and evil surrounding us. Hope you feel it too.<br/>
<br/>
You can see the paintings and the prints for yourself at the ‘Triple Trouble’ exhibition at Newport Street Gallery.</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DV3XkMiDGDT/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
